column2: select top #  a.objid, a.ra, a.dec, a.type, a.probPSF, a.petroMag_g, a.petroMag_r, a.petroRad_g, a.petroR5#_g, a.deVRad_g, a.deVRad_r, a.expRad_g, a.expRad_r, a.expAB_g, a.deVAB_g, a.expAB_r, a.deVAB_r, a.cModelMag_g, a.cModelMag_r, b.z, b.zerr, b.lumDist, b.synthG, b.synthR, b.absMagG, b.absMagR, c.logd_#, c.bmvt, c.loga_e, c.mpe from PhotoObjAll as a  join photoz as b on a.objid = b.objid  join RC3 as c on a.objid = c.objid where c.mpe > #  and a.petroMag_g < #  and a.petroMag_r < #  and a.type = #   and petror5#_g > #  and (a.petroMag_g+#+#*LOG1#(#*petroR5#_g*petroR5#_g)>#)
